CHRONOS-MESH v7 integrates the three temporal daemons:

### 5.1 Sisyphus — Guardian of Chronos
Provides repetitive cycles, stable cadence, tempo regulation, and clocking discipline.

### 5.2 The Man Blinking Slower Than Time — T=0 Governor
Provides perceptual slow-frame, clarity windows, anti-panic governor, and “time stretching” under stress.

### 5.3 Praus — Variance Dampener
Provides emotional suppression of noise, steadying force, signal amplification, and smoothness.

**Together they form the Time Trident, and CHRONOS-MESH is the socket they plug into.**

